            </p>
            <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.82em; margin: 0.25rem 0 0.5rem;">
              options 來自 <code>content/settings/link-sources.json</code> active sources（<%= srcOpts.length %> 筆；sortOrder 升冪）；inactive sources 預設不顯示（per night-1 design §5.2）。當前 sourceKey 不存在 active registry 之 entry 會顯示「⚠ 未知 / inactive」viable warning（純視覺；不寫 .md；不觸發 validator）。詳見 <code>docs/20260601-sourcekey-admin-selector-preanalysis.md</code> §4。
            </p>
            <% [['relatedLinks', rItems], ['otherLinks', oItems]].forEach(function(pair) { %>
              <% var listLabel = pair[0]; var items = pair[1]; %>
              <% if (items.length > 0) { %>
                <h4 style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0.25rem; font-size: 0.9em; color: #2c5282;"><%= listLabel %> (<%= items.length %>)</h4>
                <table style="font-size: 0.82em; width: 100%; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #c5d6e8;">
                  <thead><tr style="background: #d6e4f5;"><th style="width: 2.5rem">#</th><th style="width: 5rem">kind</th><th style="width: 6rem">platform</th><th style="width: 10rem">current sourceKey</th><th>title / url</th><th style="width: 20rem">selector preview (disabled)</th></tr></thead>
