                <p class="dry-run-warning" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">⚠️ Dry-run only. No file will be written. 若要實際寫入：VS Code 編輯 source 檔 + <code>git diff</code> + <code>git commit</code>。</p>
              </div>
              <%# Phase 20260527-night-9 Admin Write Infra Phase 3b dry-run-only UI
